de.malkusch.whoisServerList.publicSuffixList.index

Class Index

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.malkusch.whoisServerList.publicSuffixList.index.Index

  • @ThreadSafe
public abstract class Index
extends Object
    Rule index. The PublicSuffixListFactory builds the PublicSuffixList with the index defined with the property PublicSuffixListFactory.PROPERTY_INDEX. Index implementations must be thread-safe.

    markus@malkusch.de
